								Yūḥannā Dāʾūd.</summary>
                     <handNote script="Hebrew" scope="sole" />
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>2 full-page decorations: f. 1v: the name of the author in golden
									letters with a menorah and a magen David in gold on top; f. 2r:
									the title of the book, the word 'Amen', and Ps. 51:17 in golden
									letters, and a golden magen David.</p>
                        <p>F. 188v: at the end of the work, Ps. 16:8 in golden letters and a
									dove holding a branch in its beak.</p>
                     </decoNote>
